text: Part 8. Control Identifiers, Profile Strategies, and Market Profiling Templating. The legend, Paul Tudor Jones once said, Don't be a hero. Don't have an ego. Always question yourself and your ability. Don't ever feel that you are very good. The second you do, you are dead.
